title: California Court Mostly Upholds Prop. 22 in Win for Uber and Other Gig Companies
description: The decision lessens the chances that gig drivers will be considered employees in the state, but it is expected to be appealed to the state Supreme Court.

title: An A.I. Start-Up Boomed, but Now It Faces a Slowing Economy and New Rules
description: Using A.I. tools in hiring is one of the most promising and contentious uses of the technology. The experience of a company called Eightfold AI shows the challenges.
